Naples Daily multimedia journalist J. Scott Butherus and analyst John Weber are at First Baptist Academy to get you ready for Week 9 of the high school football season in Southwest Florida. 
Coach Weber talks with Lions head coach Billy Sparacio about wrapping up another 2A district title.
